{"pageProps":{"bookPath":"go","postPath":"go-basic","post":{"title":"Go: 杂项","body":"<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\">\n<div id=\"toctitle\">目录</div>\n<ul class=\"sectlevel1\">\n<li><a href=\"#_代码格式化\">代码格式化</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#_注释\">注释</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#_命名\">命名</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect1\">\n<h2 id=\"_代码格式化\">代码格式化</h2>\n<div class=\"sectionbody\">\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>很多人因为代码格式化大开嘴炮。Go 语言的开发者觉得这太无聊了，干脆用统一风格别在 Go 这里吵了吧。于是 Go\n的格式化风格就被固定下来了。<code>gofmt</code> 程序会把代码格式化为一种固定风格。其中一些细节比如：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ulist\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>使用 tab 进行缩进</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>不限制一行的长度</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>与 C、Java 等语言相比，括号更少</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect1\">\n<h2 id=\"_注释\">注释</h2>\n<div class=\"sectionbody\">\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>Go 语言支持两种风格的注释：行注释 <code>//</code> 和块注释 <code>/*  */</code>。行注释更常用，块注释主要用做包注释。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p><code>godoc</code> 通过提取 API 注释来生成 API 文档。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>函数注释通常是一个行注释，以函数名开头，后面接上一个描述此函数的句子。比如：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-go\" data-lang=\"go\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Add 把两个数先加，并返回和</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">Add</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">(i, j <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">int</span>)</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">int</span></span> {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> i + j\n}</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect1\">\n<h2 id=\"_命名\">命名</h2>\n<div class=\"sectionbody\">\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>包名通常是源码所在的目录名称。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>对于属性的获取器，getter 函数通常不是以 <code>Get</code> 开头，看起来别扭，建议直接使用属性名，比如 <code>person.Age</code>；setter\n用 <code>Set</code> 开头挺合理，于是就这样了，比如：<code>person.SetAge(12)</code>。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>如果一个接口只包含一个方法，那么通常以 <code>-er</code> 结尾，比如 <code>Reader</code>、<code>Writer</code>、<code>Formatter</code> 等等。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>返回字符串表示的方法名应为 <code>String</code>，而非 <code>ToString</code>。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>Go 语言标识符统一是驼峰式的。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","type":"adoc"},"book":{"title":"Go 基础","toc":[{"title":"基础","path":"go-basic"},{"title":"函数","path":"go-func"},{"title":"变量","path":"go-var"},{"title":"基本类型","path":"go-basic-types"},{"title":"字符串","path":"go-string"},{"title":"指针","path":"go-ptr"},{"title":"数组和切片","path":"go-array-slice"},{"title":"映射","path":"go-map"},{"title":"结构：struct","path":"go-struct"},{"title":"接口：interface","path":"go-itf"},{"title":"type 关键字","path":"go-type"},{"title":"for 语句","path":"go-for"},{"title":"if 语句","path":"go-if"},{"title":"switch 语句","path":"go-switch"},{"title":"defer 语句","path":"go-defer"},{"title":"并发","path":"go-concurrency"},{"title":"包和导入","path":"go-pkg-import"}],"path":"go"}},"__N_SSG":true}